   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-a" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(You tell what happened)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>Welcome, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. You must be fatigued from the long journey. You don't look so good.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-b" mid="11" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>I see. A terrible tempest must have passed beyond.<BR>However, the sandstorm will continue to bring new tempests until the very end.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-c" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>
Moreover, it seems that changes are coming again to Mistland and Lagendia.<BR>
Incidents always seem to spring up around you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. Indeed, just like a sandstorm.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-d" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Leaving changes in your wake…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>
Storms come as a disaster, but each land they pass is cleansed.<BR>
The two worlds, too, will continue to change with this incident.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-e" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>As always, we priestesses look forward to the changes you will bring, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-f" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>But enough of that. The flower you're holding... Was that left behind by the Frozen Dragon?<BR>It appears fragile, yet its chill is sharp enough to cut flesh.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-g" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>It seems cold enough to freeze anything, including <FONT color=#a82424>hatred</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>betrayal</FONT>... Yet contained within that ice is <FONT color=#086171>sadness</FONT> and <FONT color=#086171>memories</FONT>.<BR>Is that why it looks like such a fragile flower?<BR>Perhaps because I have seen what it contains, I get the sense that someone tried to protect it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n735_darklair_mocha-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n735_darklair_mocha-2" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Mocha$<BR>Do you think you could ever sacrifice everything for another, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>?<BR>Never mind, I don't need to ask. You have already done so much for others, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3105_dragon_buff_frozen-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
